description: Choice of the Employee to receive from their employer a document of this Document Type. This choice can originate from the choice of the employee to opt out (see `electronic_payslips_opted_out`), from the decision to open or not his or her vault (see `electronic_vault_activated`) or from the choice made the employee in his or her electronic vault to receive a document of this type in an `electronic`or `paper` format. Can be one of: `electronic`, `paper`, `null`
